```

The correlation matrix is hard to read, especially for too many variables. We can use some other packages to help. First, we can try the library `corrplot`.

```{r }
loadPkg("corrplot")
```

```{r include=T, warning=F}
corrplot(mtcarscor)
```

```{r warning=F}
